description:
To all motor enthusiasts craving a wide selection of different vehicles – we got you covered! With the Police Simulator: Patrol Officers: Garage Bundle you can add 6 cool patrol cars to your fleet – each with their own special features. 

Includes:
•	Compact Police Vehicle DLC
•	Urban Terrain Vehicle DLC
•	Guardian Police Vehicle DLC
•	Multipurpose Police Vehicle DLC
•	Surveillance Police Vehicle DLC
•	Warden Police Vehicle DLC
name: Police Simulator: Patrol Officers: Garage Bundle
